steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Database" without submenu
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jit012a" and Comment "Testing"
Then I should see the table with Name "jit012a" display
When I add new table with Name "jit012b" and Comment "Testing"
Then I should see the table with Name "jit012b" display
When I drag the table Name "jit012b" to new location with x: "200", y: "0"
When I trigger relation popup established from table Name "jit012a" to table Name "jit012b"

steps.name: When I check radio button popup Name "has many"
When I update popup with dropdown Name "Target" to value "jit012bs"
Then I should see textbox popup Name "Foreign key" has value "jit012a_id"
When I check checkbox popup Name "nullable"
When I update popup with textbox Name "Foreign key" to value "empty"
When I press Save button modal popup without wait
Then I should see inline error message of textbox label "Foreign key" has value "Foreign key can not be empty"
When I update popup with textbox Name "Foreign key" to value "jitera"
When I press Save button modal popup without wait
Then I should see the warning popup with message "Validation failed: Foreign key Foreign key must end with "_id""
When I close the modal popup
